The paper discusses the application of deep learning techniques in mobile and wireless networking, which falls under the category of computer networks and the sub-category of network architecture and design (cs.NI). The paper also extensively discusses deep learning techniques and their potential applications, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the management and optimization of network resources, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the use of deep learning in mobile applications and services, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
